```
#import "iRate.h"
```

to your AppDelegate.m?

So your AppDelegate.m should look similar to:

```
#import "AppDelegate.h"
#import "iRate.h"

@implementation AppDelegate


+ (void)initialize
{
    //configure iRate
    [iRate sharedInstance].daysUntilPrompt = 5;
    [iRate sharedInstance].usesUntilPrompt = 15;
    [iRate sharedInstance].previewMode = NO;
}
```
. No I believe there is no setting for uses. However, this is the setting for days (in case you didn't know the setting), as you mentioned.

```
[iRate sharedInstance].remindPeriod = 10;
```

I suggest being able to remind after uses should be added as a new feature.
