toddkramer:
For the sake of completeness, here is how the "weak property unpredictably set to nil" warning could be resolved.

__strong id(iRateDelegate) delegate = [self delegate];
if (delegate) {
   [delegate iRateDidDetectAppUpdate];
}

*I had to replace the "<" and ">" signs with parenthesis in __strong id iRateDelegate to avoid GitHub formatting.

This will work for the other instances of this warning as well.
