. Well, it doesn't look good to me, sorry. I believe the code should look this way:

```
        if (self.firstUsed)
        {
            if ([[NSDate date] timeIntervalSinceDate:self.firstUsed] >= self.daysUntilPrompt * SECONDS_IN_A_DAY))
            {
